{"tid":1265138,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮：G20後彭斯將發表針對中國人權演說","createTime":"2019-06-29T04:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T08:23:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9bd445a97dea49b21cb1ff48610e56a58c945334","tid":1265138,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T04:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpVDk6Ey.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpVDk6Ey.jpg&h=d23696d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（歐新社）<br />\n<br />\n美國副總統彭斯（Mike Pence）原定在6月初發表針對中國人權的演說，但後來因故延遲，白宮28日證實美國總統川普喊停了這項決定，並期待在20國集團（G20）峰會後能發表演說。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》先前報導，川普暫緩彭斯對中國的批判演說，以避免在G20峰會期間與習近平的會晤之前激怒北京。美國智庫威爾遜中心（The Wilson Center）的網站原本公布彭斯將於6月24日在該中心發表演說。<br />\n<br />\n《美國之音》報導，副總統辦公室主任肖特（Mark Short）表示，彭斯確實在與川普總統談話後，決定暫停在威爾遜中心的演講，白宮會在G20過後公布確定的演講日期。肖特也澄清，他看到一些報導指演講原本定在6月4日，但其實該演講的日期就是定在6月24日。<br />\n<br />\n對於彭斯的演講是否會圍繞在中國人權、宗教自由等方面問題，肖特指出，這是彭斯副總統的決定，彭斯去年在哈德遜研究所談了許多美國對中國的擔憂，以及對貿易協議的期望，但美國仍要關注國家安全與兩國關係，而彭斯副總統想要針對這些議題發表演說。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2837162\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2837162&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmqxdyOQTk4RMct2Rsqyof94c%3D&h=1fe9d082\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2837162&h=18784077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2837162</a>"},{"pid":"7518866d636e765d0954ac4213479e0de3196db7","tid":1265138,"uid":59919,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:05:37.000Z","msg":"g20你唔係佢面前講點落佢面<br />\n係白宮講，佢最多搵口交部出來嘴炮"},{"pid":"865c516e1a63b5daaeaec9ca16e27082d6e199eb","tid":1265138,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:19:11.000Z","msg":"又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n施壓失敗  郭文貴：彭斯六四演說「一定會發生」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1188312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1188312</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1a0d97bb7e5fd408cd42feac0bb0c249e78a7d3e","tid":1265138,"uid":230511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:24:43.000Z","msg":"《彭博》先前報導，川普<span style=\"color: red;\">暫緩</span>彭斯對中國的批判演說，以避免在G20峰會期間與習近平的會晤之前激怒北京。美國智庫威爾遜中心（The Wilson Center）的網站原本公布彭斯將於6月24日在該中心發表演說。<br />\n<br />\n完美表達咩叫暫緩，即係可以一個月都唔夠就拎返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7183cadce1b4107594517f8b875a5df8b5343d8","tid":1265138,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:29:53.000Z","msg":"我諗起好耐之前維尼去完英國派錢<br />\n<br />\n過2日就出咗英女皇同安排維尼保安嘅女警官講 Bad luck"},{"pid":"e81dcec6281fa021d37eac3414dad8f86a0750ea","tid":1265138,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd2f18efb5b2ef38e0a0c5e8576a98fa41f485f","tid":1265138,"uid":79314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:57:08.000Z","msg":"黑面白面"},{"pid":"44bfefc1f850bb1f7022c758fbd2f68703b9ffb9","tid":1265138,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:55:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba0c9a525101f4aae8fe59f29b1ea7168a9ef62c","tid":1265138,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0jn9Vd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0jn9Vd.png&h=405e8ad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a29b50b1428c65de3dd1e7c5118ca26219ac8916","tid":1265138,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T07:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces